01:00:08.704 --> 01:00:11.373
You know, I never did carry
one of those things.

01:00:13.208 --> 01:00:14.543
Why is that?

01:00:15.545 --> 01:00:16.777
Too passive.

01:00:17.614 --> 01:00:19.547
For sissies who don't want
to put any effort

01:00:19.550 --> 01:00:20.983
into what they're doing.

01:00:20.985 --> 01:00:22.317
Too clean.

01:00:23.052 --> 01:00:24.152
Right.

01:00:24.153 --> 01:00:27.655
You just prefer cutting pretty
