how I found my sister.

01:00:37.333 --> 01:00:39.300
She wasn't the first, was she?

01:00:40.469 --> 01:00:41.969
Won't be the last either.

01:00:41.972 --> 01:00:43.472
Tony: See that's
where you're wrong.

01:00:44.440 --> 01:00:46.541
You're not gonna hurt
anyone ever again.

01:00:49.244 --> 01:00:51.012
You sound real sure of yourself.

01:00:51.780 --> 01:00:54.483
