01:01:04.193 --> 01:01:05.860
The suspense is killing me.

01:01:57.547 --> 01:01:59.047
Turn the engine off.

01:02:13.028 --> 01:02:14.262
So what now?

01:02:17.065 --> 01:02:19.434
I bet you killed a lot
