to clean up afterwards

01:02:48.563 --> 01:02:51.932
alright, you sick motherfucker,
out of the car!

01:02:51.934 --> 01:02:52.967
Out!

01:02:52.969 --> 01:02:55.536
All right.
All right.

01:03:15.257 --> 01:03:16.791
I'm gonna end this,

01:03:18.161 --> 01:03:19.561
end you.

01:03:21.230 --> 01:03:22.396
Is that right?

01:03:25.134 --> 01:03:26.367
Before I do,

01:03:28.670 --> 01:03:30.639
I just gotta ask you one thing.

01:03:33.009 --> 01:03:34.208
Shoot.

01:03:38.481 --> 01:03:39.648
Why?

01:03:43.119 --> 01:03:44.219
Why?

01:03:45.987 --> 01:03:47.489
You wanna know why.

01:03:51.994 --> 01:03:53.094
All right.

01:03:54.496 --> 01:03:55.864
I'll tell you why.

01:04:28.864 --> 01:04:31.599
Because some people don't
deserve to go on living.

01:04:42.811 --> 01:04:45.447
You should've stopped talking
about what you wanted to do

01:04:46.414 --> 01:04:47.748
and done it.

01:07:31.246 --> 01:07:32.646
What's going on out here?

01:07:37.719 --> 01:07:39.586
Sorry, I didn't
mean to wake you up.

01:07:40.389 --> 01:07:41.556
Dwayne: You didn't.

01:07:42.490 --> 01:07:43.824
I just heard you crying

01:07:43.827 --> 01:07:45.927
and wanted to see what all
the commotion was about.

01:07:47.496 --> 01:07:48.963
It's a long story.

01:07:49.731 --> 01:07:51.865
Short version is I'm
locked out of my room

01:07:51.867 --> 01:07:54.302
and have no idea how
I'm gonna pay for it.

01:08:03.278 --> 01:08:04.746
Give me the long version.

01:08:06.047 --> 01:08:07.347
I got time.

01:08:09.552 --> 01:08:11.085
You sure about that?

01:08:12.554 --> 01:08:13.954
Sure I'm sure.

01:08:16.926 --> 01:08:18.091
Well...

01:08:19.795 --> 01:08:22.997
The asshole I was staying with
split town and left me here.

01:08:23.932 --> 01:08:26.167
He hit me and took
all the money,

01:08:26.734 --> 01:08:28.103
my money.

01:08:31.907 --> 01:08:33.006
How much?

01:08:33.774 --> 01:08:34.975
Enough.

01:08:38.881 --> 01:08:40.381
Why'd he take it?

01:08:41.317 --> 01:08:43.251
Because he's
a mean son of a bitch,

01:08:43.252 --> 01:08:45.819
thinks he's hot shit,
thinks he owns me.

01:08:46.453 --> 01:08:48.189
Without me
he wouldn't have a dime.

01:08:51.894 --> 01:08:53.493
What kind of work do you do?

01:08:59.435 --> 01:09:00.801
You'll judge me.

01:09:02.337 --> 01:09:03.671
I won't judge you.

01:09:12.014 --> 01:09:13.381
I'm a dancer.

01:09:15.117 --> 01:09:16.684
What kind of dancer?

01:09:18.685 --> 01:09:20.386
The kind who takes
their clothes off.

01:09:22.256 --> 01:09:23.423
Dwayne: I see.

01:09:24.658 --> 01:09:26.161
Does that bother you?

01:09:27.462 --> 01:09:29.095
I ain't easily bothered.

01:09:32.701 --> 01:09:35.368
We were in town so I
could dance at this club.

01:09:35.372 --> 01:09:38.238
He's been, like my manager
for the last year,

01:09:38.841 --> 01:09:40.640
and he just ups and leaves,

01:09:40.644 --> 01:09:42.542
everything I've been
working for.

01:09:42.944 --> 01:09:45.779
Me, I've been working that
whole time, saving up.

01:09:47.682 --> 01:09:48.881
For what?

01:09:50.853 --> 01:09:52.051
A dream.

01:09:53.956 --> 01:09:55.289
Well what dream?

01:09:59.360 --> 01:10:01.729
I've been planning on
opening a beauty salon.

01:10:02.965 --> 01:10:04.966
Wouldn't know it by
looking at me I know,

01:10:04.967 --> 01:10:07.702
but it's been a dream of mine
since I was a little girl.

01:10:10.372 --> 01:10:12.140
It's good to have dreams,

01:10:13.175 --> 01:10:14.442
to work for them.

01:10:15.911 --> 01:10:17.779
Yeah. Well...

01:10:19.247 --> 01:10:22.050
It's all gone now,
along with that money.

01:10:22.585 --> 01:10:24.085
Dwayne: Don't talk like that.

01:10:26.188 --> 01:10:28.922
There's always a way,
if you work for it.

01:10:30.993 --> 01:10:32.260
How can I say that

01:10:32.261 --> 01:10:34.395
when I can't even pay
for my own damn room?

01:10:34.396 --> 01:10:36.331
I haven't got
a goddamn cent on me.

01:10:45.274 --> 01:10:46.474
I'll tell you what.

01:10:47.443 --> 01:10:49.010
You stay with me tonight.

01:10:49.712 --> 01:10:52.313
You can even have the bed,
and I'll sleep on the floor.

01:10:53.282 --> 01:10:56.917
And in the morning we'll...
Figure out your situation.

01:10:59.721 --> 01:11:01.588
No, I couldn't put
you out like that.

01:11:02.925 --> 01:11:04.492
It ain't putting anyone out.

01:11:05.461 --> 01:11:06.961
I'd be glad to help.

01:11:08.029 --> 01:11:10.465
Plus the floor ain't
much less comfortable

01:11:10.466 --> 01:11:12.100
than the bed anyhow.

01:11:13.402 --> 01:11:14.836
And I'll be a gentleman,

01:11:15.304 --> 01:11:16.537
scout's honor.

01:11:19.707 --> 01:11:20.942
You sure?

01:11:22.478 --> 01:11:24.177
I ain't gonna offer again.

01:11:28.751 --> 01:11:30.717
Yeah. Okay.

01:11:31.220 --> 01:11:32.453
Thanks.

01:11:32.454 --> 01:11:33.720
Dwayne: Don't mention it.

01:11:34.155 --> 01:11:35.323
Come on.

01:11:52.507 --> 01:11:54.007
It ain't exactly the Ritz,

01:11:54.010 --> 01:11:57.078
but the bed's clean and I
don't have cooties or nothing.

01:11:57.979 --> 01:11:59.314
Good to know.

01:12:03.918 --> 01:12:05.353
Make yourself at home.

01:12:19.435 --> 01:12:21.502
That can't be comfortable.

01:12:22.438 --> 01:12:24.538
I'm just as fine
here as I am anywhere,

01:12:24.541 --> 01:12:25.739
believe me.

01:12:29.511 --> 01:12:31.279
So, what about you?

01:12:33.047 --> 01:12:34.515
What about me?

01:12:34.983 --> 01:12:36.884
What were you doing
in this shitty motel?

01:12:40.555 --> 01:12:42.256
It's where I feel comfortable.

01:12:43.658 --> 01:12:45.092
You traveling?

01:12:45.793 --> 01:12:47.127
Dwayne: You could say that.

01:12:48.697 --> 01:12:51.298
I'm always traveling, drifting.

01:12:52.734 --> 01:12:55.069
Never really felt at
home in any one place.

01:12:56.537 --> 01:12:57.704
Me either.

01:12:59.207 --> 01:13:01.408
So I figure I'll
just keep on drifting

01:13:01.844 --> 01:13:03.944
until I find something
that makes me wanna stop,

01:13:04.813 --> 01:13:06.079
know what I mean?

01:13:06.715 --> 01:13:08.082
Yeah, I think I do.

01:13:08.083 --> 01:13:09.817
Maybe that's what I should do.

01:13:09.819 --> 01:13:12.252
What you should do is
open up that beauty salon.

01:13:12.255 --> 01:13:13.755
That's what you should do.

01:13:14.256 --> 01:13:16.423
Yeah, someday.

01:13:16.759 --> 01:13:18.126
Yeah, you'll do it.

01:13:18.894 --> 01:13:20.627
You just gotta keep motoring on.

01:13:22.264 --> 01:13:23.898
You know what your destiny is.

01:13:25.734 --> 01:13:29.069
You just gotta keep moving
forward and you'll get there.

01:13:31.340 --> 01:13:32.774
Nothing's gonna stop you,

01:13:33.442 --> 01:13:34.742
no one.

01:13:36.444 --> 01:13:38.011
No one's ever stopped me.

01:13:40.548 --> 01:13:41.916
What's your destiny?

01:13:46.454 --> 01:13:48.655
I don't think I can
tell you that just yet.

01:13:49.524 --> 01:13:50.591
Why not?

01:13:52.761 --> 01:13:54.261
I don't have the answer.

01:13:55.898 --> 01:13:56.997
Not yet.

01:14:00.068 --> 01:14:01.469
I'm getting closer.

01:14:02.537 --> 01:14:04.271
Will you tell me
when you do know?

01:14:05.106 --> 01:14:06.340
Sure I will.

01:14:08.076 --> 01:14:10.144
I'm still trying to figure out
what mine is.

01:14:14.315 --> 01:14:16.216
You look like a
girl I once knew.

01:14:16.819 --> 01:14:18.286
Roxy: Oh yeah, who's that?

01:14:19.654 --> 01:14:20.822
Carol Ann.

01:14:22.957 --> 01:14:24.625
A girl I almost married.

01:14:27.895 --> 01:14:29.630
She had hair just like yours.

01:14:30.798 --> 01:14:33.400
This thing?

01:14:34.970 --> 01:14:36.369
I just wear it for work.

01:14:36.904 --> 01:14:38.872
Most men have
a thing for blondes.

01:14:40.141 --> 01:14:41.341
Yeah.

01:14:45.680 --> 01:14:48.181
So... what happened?

01:14:50.118 --> 01:14:51.351
What?

01:14:51.787 --> 01:14:53.087
Roxy: What happened?

01:14:53.689 --> 01:14:56.189
- To what?
- The girl you were gonna marry.

01:15:00.828 --> 01:15:02.162
She broke my heart.

01:15:04.966 --> 01:15:06.033
Sorry.

01:15:08.136 --> 01:15:09.403
It's all right.

01:15:10.872 --> 01:15:12.573
She got what she deserved.

01:15:15.676 --> 01:15:16.777
And so did I.

01:15:22.216 --> 01:15:23.917
I don't think I
caught your name.

01:15:25.052 --> 01:15:27.421
Roxy. What's yours?

01:15:27.855 --> 01:15:29.055
Dwayne.

01:15:29.057 --> 01:15:31.158
Dwayne. I like that.

01:15:31.159 --> 01:15:32.726
Sounds like a rock
and roll singer.

01:15:35.396 --> 01:15:37.765
You don't wanna hear
me sing, that's for sure.

01:15:38.399 --> 01:15:40.167
Bust every window
out of this joint.

01:15:40.168 --> 01:15:43.703
All right, I'll
take your word for it.

01:15:47.743 --> 01:15:49.143
Well you must be tired.

01:15:50.511 --> 01:15:51.912
I'll let you rest.

01:16:09.597 --> 01:16:12.132
Thanks again for helping me out.

01:16:13.201 --> 01:16:14.635
It's no trouble.

01:16:15.337 --> 01:16:17.637
You just get some sleep
and we'll talk in the morning.

01:16:21.409 --> 01:16:22.609
Night, Dwayne.

01:16:23.377 --> 01:16:24.744
Goodnight, Roxy.

01:17:14.328 --> 01:17:15.496
Morning.

01:17:16.497 --> 01:17:17.564
Morning.

01:17:19.067 --> 01:17:20.301
How'd you sleep?

01:17:21.670 --> 01:17:23.337
Like the dead.

01:17:25.841 --> 01:17:27.073
Good.

01:17:28.176 --> 01:17:29.377
You?

01:17:31.345 --> 01:17:32.813
I don't sleep much.

01:17:34.448 --> 01:17:35.582
Oh.

01:17:39.154 --> 01:17:40.520
I was thinking.

01:17:41.288 --> 01:17:42.689
Roxy: About what?

01:17:43.257 --> 01:17:44.492
That guy.

01:17:45.627 --> 01:17:47.228
Took all that money from you.

01:17:48.462 --> 01:17:49.596
Yeah.

01:17:50.865 --> 01:17:52.332
What's his name?

01:17:54.368 --> 01:17:55.502
Sug.

01:17:56.805 --> 01:17:57.938
Sug what?

01:17:59.841 --> 01:18:01.207
Sug white.

01:18:01.810 --> 01:18:03.043
Sug white?

01:18:05.881 --> 01:18:07.213
That's what he goes by.

01:18:07.216 --> 01:18:09.082
I don't know what
his real name is.

01:18:09.650 --> 01:18:12.185
You got any idea where Sug
might've ran off to?

01:18:14.122 --> 01:18:16.189
- Pretty good one.

01:18:16.192 --> 01:18:17.192
Where?

01:18:19.060 --> 01:18:21.395
He has this big house in
the suburbs where he stays

01:18:21.396 --> 01:18:23.396
with some of his people.

01:18:24.365 --> 01:18:25.599
Where is it?

01:18:26.501 --> 01:18:28.402
It's a couple hours from here.

01:18:28.404 --> 01:18:31.439
That's why we were staying
here while I was... working.

01:18:34.576 --> 01:18:36.310
And you're really sure
he's there?

01:18:37.979 --> 01:18:40.381
I don't know, but I bet he is.

01:18:40.815 --> 01:18:42.649
He knows I can't go back there.

01:18:42.652 --> 01:18:44.784
Kick my ass if I ever
showed up there again.

01:18:47.922 --> 01:18:49.622
You're not gonna show up there.

01:18:51.760 --> 01:18:53.094
What do you mean?

01:18:54.996 --> 01:18:56.262
I am.

01:18:58.934 --> 01:19:00.467
Why?

01:19:01.069 --> 01:19:02.235
Well...

01:19:02.938 --> 01:19:04.805
When someone takes what's yours,

01:19:05.506 --> 01:19:07.173
you have a right to get it back.

01:19:10.244 --> 01:19:11.746
But how would you do it?

01:19:12.780 --> 01:19:14.247
Let me worry about that.

01:19:14.615 --> 01:19:16.317
You just tell me
how to get there.

01:19:17.786 --> 01:19:19.353
I won't let them hurt you.

01:19:20.255 --> 01:19:21.689
They won't even
know you're there.

01:19:26.027 --> 01:19:27.360
I don't know.

01:19:28.529 --> 01:19:30.797
You still wanna open up
that beauty salon, don't you?

01:19:33.368 --> 01:19:34.534
Yeah.

01:19:35.069 --> 01:19:36.636
That's what I thought.

01:19:37.072 --> 01:19:39.439
Now let's go get some food
and we'll hit the road.

01:19:40.242 --> 01:19:42.877
I'll have a few words
with... Sug.

01:19:44.979 --> 01:19:46.113
All right.

01:19:56.925 --> 01:19:58.125
So where you from?

01:19:59.927 --> 01:20:01.662
Brownwood, Texas.

01:20:02.163 --> 01:20:05.733
- Never been there.
- Don't bother. Nothing to see.

01:20:06.835 --> 01:20:08.536
How long did you live there?

01:20:09.671 --> 01:20:10.904
Long enough.

01:20:11.840 --> 01:20:15.876
And then after the
woman I loved... left,

01:20:16.677 --> 01:20:18.479
I decided to hit the road.

01:20:19.747 --> 01:20:21.181
What about your family?

01:20:22.751 --> 01:20:24.051
No family.

01:20:25.654 --> 01:20:27.054
My folks are dead.

01:20:28.957 --> 01:20:30.056
Oh.

01:20:31.193 --> 01:20:32.426
What happened?

01:20:34.796 --> 01:20:36.497
They both died when I was a kid.

01:20:38.632 --> 01:20:39.966
My daddy used to get drunk

01:20:39.969 --> 01:20:42.036
at the same country
western bar every night,

01:20:43.137 --> 01:20:46.073
get in fights, get kicked out.

01:20:47.475 --> 01:20:50.176
Then he'd come home
and beat up on my mama and me.

01:20:51.947 --> 01:20:53.713
And it went on
that way for years.

01:20:55.550 --> 01:20:56.884
Then one night...

01:20:58.353 --> 01:21:00.554
Someone cut his brakes
while he was in the bar.

01:21:03.792 --> 01:21:05.225
It just so happened

01:21:05.228 --> 01:21:07.694
when mama got dropped off
to check up on him,

01:21:07.697 --> 01:21:09.496
make sure he was all right,

01:21:09.497 --> 01:21:11.198
and drive his truck home,

01:21:13.467 --> 01:21:14.801
it was raining,

01:21:15.337 --> 01:21:16.337
hard to see,

01:21:18.340 --> 01:21:20.940
and there was this bridge
between our house and the bar.

01:21:23.345 --> 01:21:25.045
The truck went right
off the bridge.

01:21:25.913 --> 01:21:27.381
They both drowned.

01:21:28.515 --> 01:21:29.783
Oh my god.

01:21:30.217 --> 01:21:32.086
Did they ever catch
the guy who did it?

01:21:34.521 --> 01:21:35.622
No.

01:21:38.659 --> 01:21:39.926
I'm sorry.

01:21:40.494 --> 01:21:42.162
Nothing to be sorry for.

01:21:43.198 --> 01:21:44.765
What's done is done.

01:21:47.702 --> 01:21:49.569
I went to live with
my gram after that.

01:21:49.572 --> 01:21:51.404
She was a good woman.

01:21:53.341 --> 01:21:55.009
After she passed away she...

01:21:55.777 --> 01:21:57.344
Left me everything she had,

01:21:58.747 --> 01:22:00.613
including this car
she never drove.

01:22:02.283 --> 01:22:04.251
And instead of buying
some chunk of land,

01:22:04.719 --> 01:22:06.252
I decided to see the world,

01:22:07.055 --> 01:22:08.988
maybe find a woman
that was worth loving.

01:22:10.024 --> 01:22:11.524
And how's that been?

01:22:13.795 --> 01:22:15.095
Disappointing.

01:22:16.131 --> 01:22:17.430
Why's that?

01:22:18.033 --> 01:22:21.167
People let you down
time and again.

01:22:22.636 --> 01:22:24.438
There's a lot of
ugliness in the world.

01:22:25.707 --> 01:22:26.940
Too much.

01:22:28.542 --> 01:22:29.643
Matter of fact,

01:22:29.645 --> 01:22:31.845
you're the first pretty thing
I've seen in a long time.

01:22:33.280 --> 01:22:34.515
I'm not pretty.

01:22:34.882 --> 01:22:36.283
Sure you are.

01:22:36.952 --> 01:22:39.153
Pretty's not just
on the outside, you know.

01:22:40.587 --> 01:22:42.122
But you've got both.

01:22:43.490 --> 01:22:44.725
Well, thanks.

01:22:45.894 --> 01:22:47.461
Just speaking the truth.

01:22:51.298 --> 01:22:53.458
Would you ever think about
trying to get married again?

01:22:54.903 --> 01:22:56.036
I always thought

01:22:56.237 --> 01:22:58.117
