01:42:17.797 --> 01:42:19.297
so I ended it.

01:42:23.804 --> 01:42:25.404
After she was gone,

01:42:26.439 --> 01:42:28.207
I kept seeing her too.

01:42:31.011 --> 01:42:32.478
Everywhere.

01:42:34.480 --> 01:42:35.715
Every woman.

01:42:40.154 --> 01:42:41.554
Until I met you.

01:42:44.024 --> 01:42:45.824
You won't see her again.

01:42:46.926 --> 01:42:48.728
I'll make sure you don't.

01:43:05.845 --> 01:43:07.012
Dwayne?

01:43:08.015 --> 01:43:09.181
Yeah?

01:43:12.552 --> 01:43:14.886
Would you ever think
about marrying me one day

01:43:14.889 --> 01:43:16.555
if everything worked out?

01:43:18.292 --> 01:43:19.591
I don't know.

01:43:23.363 --> 01:43:25.064
What if I loved you,

01:43:25.065 --> 01:43:26.899
and what if you loved me?

01:43:33.873 --> 01:43:35.975
The last time I
almost got married,

01:43:37.743 --> 01:43:39.244
things ended bad.

01:43:41.547 --> 01:43:42.747
Real bad.

01:43:45.652 --> 01:43:47.920
I don't wanna make
that same mistake twice.

01:43:54.994 --> 01:43:57.395
- I understand. I'm sorry.
- Don't be sorry.

01:44:00.266 --> 01:44:02.301
Just give me a while
to think, okay?

01:44:03.436 --> 01:44:04.670
Okay.

01:44:38.771 --> 01:44:40.171
You ready for this?

01:44:41.774 --> 01:44:43.442
As ready as I'll ever be.

01:44:44.978 --> 01:44:46.378
Well let's go.

01:45:11.438 --> 01:45:14.006
Do you, Roxanne McLean,

01:45:14.007 --> 01:45:16.141
take this man, Dwayne Duncan,

01:45:16.144 --> 01:45:18.644
to be your lawfully
wedded husband

01:45:18.645 --> 01:45:20.578
and hunk,
a hunk of burning love,

01:45:21.081 --> 01:45:22.881
to have and to hold,

01:45:23.516 --> 01:45:25.318
in sickness and in health,

01:45:25.319 --> 01:45:27.420
for better or for worse,

01:45:27.421 --> 01:45:29.055
'til death do you part?

01:45:29.789 --> 01:45:30.823
I do.

01:45:30.824 --> 01:45:32.824
Elvis: Rocking, baby doll!

01:45:32.827 --> 01:45:35.394
And do you, Dwayne Duncan,

01:45:36.162 --> 01:45:38.863
do you take this
woman, Roxanne McLean,

01:45:38.865 --> 01:45:41.033
to be your lawfully wedded wife,

01:45:41.702 --> 01:45:43.769
to have and to hold

01:45:43.770 --> 01:45:45.470
in sickness and in health,

01:45:45.472 --> 01:45:46.939
for better or for worse,

01:45:46.940 --> 01:45:48.506
'til death do you part?

01:45:59.853 --> 01:46:01.186
What's it gonna be, partner?

01:46:15.202 --> 01:46:16.402
Excuse us.

01:46:20.039 --> 01:46:21.407
Goddamn kids.

01:46:26.380 --> 01:46:28.881
Hey. What is it?
What's wrong?

01:46:30.516 --> 01:46:31.817
It's no good.

01:46:33.854 --> 01:46:37.489
- What do you mean?
- I mean it's no good.

01:46:38.992 --> 01:46:41.159
It'll never work.

01:46:42.328 --> 01:46:44.497
How can you say that?
I love you.

01:46:46.399 --> 01:46:49.502
I've been looking
for you my whole life.

01:46:50.904 --> 01:46:52.337
You're beautiful.

01:46:52.738 --> 01:46:56.007
And I thought I was cut out
for all this, but I'm not!

01:46:57.411 --> 01:46:58.844
I'm not like you.

01:46:59.845 --> 01:47:01.146
I will hurt you,

01:47:02.082 --> 01:47:03.815
just like I hurt Carol Ann

01:47:04.251 --> 01:47:05.818
after she hurt me.

01:47:07.386 --> 01:47:08.988
You won't hurt me.

01:47:09.622 --> 01:47:11.356
I've been hurt
plenty in the past,

01:47:11.359 --> 01:47:15.027
but you make me feel
like no one ever has.

01:47:16.229 --> 01:47:17.762
You saved me.

01:47:19.966 --> 01:47:21.833
I don't wanna live without you.

01:47:25.738 --> 01:47:27.338
I know you're scared.

01:47:28.375 --> 01:47:29.675
Just trust me.

01:47:30.243 --> 01:47:31.510
Trust yourself.

01:47:33.113 --> 01:47:34.712
We'll be okay, I promise.

01:47:41.720 --> 01:47:42.921
What's it gonna be, kids?

01:47:42.923 --> 01:47:45.724
I got 14 more ceremonies
to do today.

01:48:02.074 --> 01:48:04.510
Now reach in my
pocket and grab the key.

01:48:04.511 --> 01:48:05.610
Not that one.

01:48:05.613 --> 01:48:06.945
The other one.

01:48:06.948 --> 01:48:08.480
Got it.

01:48:08.483 --> 01:48:10.649
Now open the door
before my arms fall off.

01:48:17.323 --> 01:48:18.890
It's official now!

01:48:27.501 --> 01:48:29.001
I think this is it.

01:48:29.636 --> 01:48:30.869
What?

01:48:32.372 --> 01:48:33.572
My destiny.

01:48:35.108 --> 01:48:36.242
And yours.

01:48:38.677 --> 01:48:40.045
I think you're right.

01:48:42.047 --> 01:48:44.850
And now I'm gonna get
out of this dress,

01:48:45.351 --> 01:48:48.253
and you and me are gonna
consummate our marriage.

01:48:49.189 --> 01:48:50.588
I'll be right back.

01:49:02.302 --> 01:49:03.636
Roxy: <i> Close that door.</i>

01:49:03.637 --> 01:49:05.570
<i>I don't want the whole
hotel to hear us.</i>

01:49:13.313 --> 01:49:14.880
<i>Baby, I'm almost ready.</i>

01:49:15.381 --> 01:49:17.416
<i>You ready to fulfill my destiny?</i>

01:49:24.858 --> 01:49:26.091
Yes, I am.

01:49:32.164 --> 01:49:33.998
Roxy: <i> I love you, you know?</i>

01:49:34.501 --> 01:49:35.900
Dwayne: <i> I know.</i>

01:49:37.404 --> 01:49:39.337
<i>There ain't nowhere
to go from here.</i>

01:49:40.707 --> 01:49:42.274
Roxy: <i> What do you mean?</i>

01:49:42.908 --> 01:49:44.109
<i>No!</i>

01:49:46.412 --> 01:49:47.979
<i>You don't have to.</i>

01:49:48.914 --> 01:49:50.649
Dwayne: <i> Yes, I do.</i>

01:49:51.585 --> 01:49:53.118
<i>That's what I am.</i>

01:49:55.287 --> 01:49:56.822
<i>There ain't no changing that.</i>

